## Route Generation with Waymaker
- Routes are **automatically generated** by Waymaker and available via the `Controllers` object.
- Do **not** hardcode route URLs or manually construct paths.
- Use the auto-imported `Controllers` object:
  ```ts
  // Navigation links
  <Link :href="Controllers.ProjectController.index()">Projects</Link>
  <Link :href="Controllers.ProjectController.show({ project: projectId })">View Project</Link>
  
  // Form submissions
  form.post(Controllers.ProjectController.store())
  form.patch(Controllers.ProjectController.update({ project: project.id }))
  ```
- Route naming follows: `Controllers.{ControllerName}.{methodName}(parameters?)`
- Parameters are passed as objects when needed.